title: 20 Min INTERMEDIATE CALISTHENICS WORKOUT at Home | No Equipment
description:
Follow Along with this no equipment full body intermediate Calisthenics workout you can do at home. The 20 minute workout includes the best intermediate Calisthenics exercises for building strength, skill and mobility. Include this in your Calisthenics training for enhanced results.
